# Implementation Plan - Air Quality Dashboard Initialization

## Goal
Initialize the project structure and implement Phase 1. We are expanding the scope to support **all major cities** dynamically, making this a portfolio-grade project that demonstrates scalability and API integration.

## User Review Required
- **Mock Data Strategy**: For the "historical" data simulation, I will generate data for ~10 major global cities (e.g., Delhi, Mumbai, New York, London, Tokyo) to show variety. The real-time part will fetch from *any* city available in OpenAQ.
- **Dependencies**: Added `requests` for API calls.

